io.reinert.requestor

Class SerializedRequestImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.reinert.requestor.SerializedRequestImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Request, SerializedRequest

    public class SerializedRequestImpl
extends Object
implements SerializedRequest
    Represents a request with its payload already serialized.

    This is the final form of a request before it's sent to the server.

    Author:
    Danilo Reinert
